  {
    "client_msg_id": "41dbb380-059c-43a0-921d-8563f8dfad31",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Finding an interface *satisfying* is something different though, and might hold more promise. Borrowing strategies from video games to get people addicted to interacting with code could improve the experience of coding. That opens a whole new set of philosophical questions though.",
